Today, at Xbox Games Showcase and Starfield Direct, we showed the exciting =
future for players and game creators =E2=80=93 dozens of new games, a new 1=
TB Series S console and new ways for players to get their games anywhere wi=
th PC Game Pass coming to NVIDIA GeForce NOW later this year. After our dou=
