 and just last quarter we saw a 46% increase year over year in people playi=
ng PC games on Game Pass. Game Pass continues to grow =E2=80=93 our revenue=
 from subscriptions overall reached nearly $1 billion last quarter.

We=E2=80=99re excited about the future of Xbox, and we see the opportunity =
